Kim Kardashian ’s bum has broken the internet countless times so is so it’s safe to say she’s used to having the best bum in the family. 
But now she may have to relinquish her booty crown to Rob Kardashian’s fiancé Blac Chyna . 
You see, the mum of two has stripped off for a new photoshoot covered in tribal white paint – and it’s remarkably similar to one of Kim’s famous shoots. 
Wearing white and green body paint – and nothing else – Blac Chyna shared the photos on Instagram writing: “Queen.” 
The new mum wears her hair dark and natural for the stunning pictures. 
She wore gold-toned makeup to highlight her face with a smokey eye and high-shine lips.
